> offset was added because of issue #969. Why are we reverting it?

We are breaking Java libraries by changing the type of the value we return. 

@rnewson : Please -1 if you think we shouldn't revert it. I am not sure what would be the right course of action in this case.

@garrensmith you broke Jenkins.

Good place to start: https://builds.apache.org/blue/organizations/jenkins/CouchDB/detail/master/499/pipeline

Some of those are being killed because test runs are taking > 1h. Ycan relax that delay in Jenkinsfile but that's not great that our tests are taking 1h
